descriptionHtml:
[b][color=grey]STORYLINE[/color][/b]
Larrius Maricus, Immperial, who dropped out of the Arcane University in Cyrodill. The quality of education dropped since the Great War. He was heading to the College of Winterhold.

[img]http://i286.photobucket.com/albums/ll97/Mshai85/razmak.jpg[/img]

[b][color=grey]DESCRIPTION[/color][/b]
You start as an apprentice mage who has just reached WInterhold. The main quest is disabled. Your map is completely empty. You know nothing about the Helgen dragon incident.
author: Moe97
